01:04:31.320 --> 01:04:36.500
Before we were approached by JC at the deal, in fact, before Dark Skies was even finished,

01:04:36.560 --> 01:04:39.640
we were still scouting Dark Skies, doing location scouting.

01:04:40.180 --> 01:04:42.540
This is, you're about to, I know what you're going to do.

