This is a location scout during the pilot that was directed by Toby Hooper,

01:04:50.060 --> 01:04:55.800
who we all know is the director of Texas Chainsaw Massacre and the director of Poltergeist.

01:04:56.180 --> 01:04:59.840
And Brent and I had managed, through sheer luck because of his relationship,

01:05:00.160 --> 01:05:01.980
to get him hired to direct our pilot.

01:05:02.460 --> 01:05:05.460
And he wanted to, you know, in Hollywood, you got to protect your material.

01:05:05.960 --> 01:05:08.420
There were some directors we met with that said,

01:05:08.500 --> 01:05:10.480
okay, I'm going to cut the first 45 pages.

