That's one of the hardest things about disclosure, because I don't feel that there is an objective

03:00:42.120 --> 03:00:44.420
truth in all of this.

03:00:45.080 --> 03:00:49.580
Um, I, you know, I had mentioned before a couple of times in my life, I've had these

