So that Rashomon effect of like anything that happens, you see this a lot with people that

03:01:42.160 --> 03:01:43.820
have UFO experiences, right?

03:01:43.940 --> 03:01:49.120
When you're, you're, you're, you're experiencing the phenomenon, you're seeing it through your

03:01:49.120 --> 03:01:50.140
filter, right?

